{"tid":1557362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教大學生會會長入稟高院 要求法庭頒令港鐵披露8.31太子荔枝角站CCTV紀錄","createTime":"2019-09-10T05:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T06:11:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58861dac2e73e39cf8af934ed126e4b2a1132299","tid":1557362,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"8.31晚上有防暴警察及速龍小隊進入港鐵太子站月台執法，其後並封鎖太子站，香港教育大學學生會會長梁耀霆日前入稟高等法院，若有人即將提出申索，可根據《高等法院規則》於法律程序展開前，要求法庭頒令非該法律程序一方披露文件。梁要求港鐵披露8月31 日晚上至凌晨時分太子站及荔枝角站所有閉路電視紀錄，以供代表律師檢查及保存副本，港鐵須於頒令後7天內執行有關命令，<span style=\"color: red;\">高院將於下周一(16日)進行指示聆訊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n申請人梁耀霆，答辯人香港鐵路有限公司。原告根據《高等法院規則》第42條及第24號命令第7A條規則，申請原訴傳票，要求答辯人向代表原告的律師行披露<span style=\"color: red;\">2019年8月31日晚上9時半至翌日凌晨1時45分位於港鐵太子站的所有閉路電視紀綠，以及2019年9月1日凌晨12時30分至凌晨2時位於港鐵荔枝角站所有閉路電視紀錄</span>，以供代表律師檢查及保存副本，並要求答辯人須於法庭頒令起7天內盡快執行有關命令。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據司法機構網頁顯示，高等法院將於下周一(16日)早上9時半就是次申請進行法庭指示聆訊，主審法官為周家明，估計需時30分鐘。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2448255/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2448255%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=4076f4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2448255/</a>"},{"pid":"a380df0213329de7dad1793a574c54b20870130f","tid":1557362,"uid":221336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後全部人同我推文個時加埋新屋嶺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以俾呢件事spin走！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如: <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831<br />\n新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"df525cd58db0f8680967dcc386e8ed23fb3e0aed","tid":1557362,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fdfcfca7b38b1e4104f7e668fa10b3c0257dc5","tid":1557362,"uid":264308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44901b2b343c984cf5e878f0d171fa7c1dfa6d50","tid":1557362,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53a3a7a00187bdf85235601401a552bd232d373","tid":1557362,"uid":160147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"有速龍小隊昨晚（8月31日）衝入太子站，並拘捕約40名站內人士；香港教育大學學生會今日（1日）公布，會長梁耀霆昨晚同於太子站被捕，現被拘留於葵涌警署，暫未知罪名。<br />\n<br />\n學生會同時譴責警察使用過份武力，以及在港鐵車廂內毆打普通乘客的行為。"},{"pid":"b46cf6fbcdc4ff405985a974e9737200f500ec20","tid":1557362,"uid":25573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"會長好耶<img src=\"/assets/